            <title>[PIG-4014] Fix Rank e2e test failures on tez</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4014</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Rank e2e tests all fail once we enable multiple parallelism (part of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3846&quot; title=&quot;Implement automatic reducer parallelism&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3846&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3846&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
